TITLE: Implementing Post Resolvers in RedwoodJS Service (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code provides the typed implementation (resolvers) for the GraphQL queries and mutations defined in `posts.sdl.ts`. Located in `api/src/services/posts/posts.ts`, it exports typed functions (`posts`, `post`, `createPost`, `updatePost`, `deletePost`) using generated types (`QueryResolvers`, `MutationResolvers`) for enhanced type safety. These functions interact with the database via Prisma Client (`db`) for CRUD operations. Redwood maps these service functions to the GraphQL schema.
