TITLE: Secured AdminPosts Service for User-Scoped CRUD (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet provides the backend implementation for admin-only post CRUD in the adminPosts service under RedwoodJS. Each operation is restricted to the adminâ€™s own posts by filtering with context.currentUser.id, and supports full create, update, delete, and fetch by id or collection. Prismaâ€™s findFirst() is used for flexible querying with multiple conditions. It requires RedwoodJS, Prisma, and appropriate context for authentication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/emelleby/docwood/blob/main/docs/content/02_tutorial/10_chapter7/api-side-currentuser.md#_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: javascript
