TITLE: Adding Post-Login Navigation in SigninPage using JSX
DESCRIPTION: This snippet completes the sign-in flow in the `SigninPage` component. It imports `navigate` and `routes` from `@redwoodjs/router`. Upon successful login (within the `.then` block of the `logIn` promise), it uses `navigate(routes.home())` to redirect the user to the home page.
SOURCE: https://github.com/emelleby/docwood/blob/main/docs/content/04_how-to/gotrue-auth.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: jsx
