TITLE: Defining GraphQL Schema with Role-Based Auth for deleteComment - RedwoodJS - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code defines the GraphQL schema for the comments API in a RedwoodJS project. It demonstrates how to use the @requireAuth directive with a roles argument to restrict the deleteComment mutation to users in the moderator role, while createComment remains open to unauthenticated users via @skipAuth. The schema includes Comment types, Query and Mutation definitions, and input types for creating and updating comments. Requires RedwoodJS, GraphQL and authentication setup.
