TITLE: Mocking GraphQL Comment Mutation in Storybook (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Implements TypeScript type-safe mocking for the CreateCommentMutation within a Storybook story. By specifying the mutation and variable types in 'mockGraphQLMutation', it ensures responses align with GraphQL expectations, simulates a delay, and constructs a mock comment response. This setup relies on type exports from 'types/graphql' and can verify UI behavior for asynchronous submissions, disabled states, and error handling.
