TITLE: Registering and Using a Fragment with useRegisteredFragment Hook - RedwoodJS with Apollo - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates registering a BookInfo fragment and extracting the useRegisteredFragment hook. Provides a complete component fetching and rendering book data by id using the Apollo Client cache. The useRegisteredFragment hook delivers live, up-to-date fragment data and a 'complete' boolean indicating availability. Requires @redwoodjs/web/apollo, GraphQL fragment declaration, and React setup. Input: book id; Output: rendered book fields if data is complete.
