TITLE: Handling Async Authentication in Sign In Form with RedwoodJS Auth in JSX
DESCRIPTION: This upgrade to the SigninPage's 'onSubmit' handler implements asynchronous sign in using the 'logIn' method from RedwoodJS Auth. On submit, it awaits 'logIn' with an object containing 'email' and 'password'. On error, it sets the error message in state. Dependencies include '@redwoodjs/forms', 'src/auth', and React. Inputs come from the form fields, and successful login handling is left to the developer.
