TITLE: Testing Business Rule: Updating Already Delivered Order in RedwoodJS Webhook (JSX)
DESCRIPTION: This JSX test scenario verifies a business rule within a RedwoodJS webhook handler: an order that is already 'DELIVERED' cannot be updated to 'DELIVERED' again. It uses scenario data for a delivered order, mocks a signed webhook event attempting the redundant update, invokes the handler, and asserts a 500 status code, the presence of an 'error' property in the response body, and a specific error message. This snippet also closes the `describe` block for the test suite.
SOURCE: https://github.com/emelleby/docwood/blob/main/docs/content/03_reference/docs/serverless-functions.md#_snippet_25

LANGUAGE: jsx
