TITLE: Testing Article Summary Rendering with RedwoodJS Test Utilities in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript-based snippet implements similar tests as the JavaScript example, verifying the correct rendering of both full and truncated article body within the Article component using RedwoodJS utilities. It demonstrates typing flexibility, but otherwise shares the same input structure, props, and expected outputs as the JavaScript tests. Dependencies are @redwoodjs/testing and the Article component; parameters center around the article object and optional summary prop, with outputs validated via DOM assertions and limitations as described previously.
