TITLE: Configuring Directives in RedwoodJS GraphQL Handler (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet shows the setup for the RedwoodJS GraphQL handler (`api/src/functions/graphql.ts`). It imports directives located in `src/directives` and passes them to the `createGraphQLHandler` function via the `directives` property in the configuration object. This automatically integrates the defined directives into the GraphQL schema.
